{"tid":1666272,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"人民日報文章批評有香港中學教材將黃之鋒列為名人系列","createTime":"2019-10-21T02:20:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-21T22:01:12.000Z","uid":130626,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9f86d4073459bfc6f193c9462684b29dba6758cc","tid":1666272,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T02:20:53.000Z","msg":"內地人民日報發表評論文章，提到網上有圖片顯示，香港有中學教材將黃之鋒列入「中華傳統美德格言及名人系列」，對黃之鋒所作所為大加讚賞，評論批評，這部教材是「荒謬」。<br />\n<br />\n評論認為，稍有常識的人都知道，黃之鋒是公認的「港獨」分子，不久前還跑到西方國家，乞求制裁自己的同胞，形容他與「中華傳統美德」扯不上絲毫關係。<br />\n<br />\n評論又說，通識教育教材刻意放大香港與內地矛盾，鼓動學生通過「非制度化途徑」表達訴求，形容有教師上課不講知識、不談規律，夾帶私貨、觀點先行。<br />\n<br />\n評論認為，教育必須牢牢紮根本國的文明母體，才能枝繁葉茂，又指出傳承中華優秀文化，強化國民身份認同，才能讓香港年輕人深刻認識到自己和香港從何而來、向何處去。<br />\n<br />\n黃之鋒在區議會選舉報名參選南區海怡西選區，同區參選人有新民黨陳家珮。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/5xb1p3cdX5dRTJdvGvqfcg--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2019-10/9b7680c0-f387-11e9-9f7f-36d7b8689756\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F5xb1p3cdX5dRTJdvGvqfcg--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2019-10%2F9b7680c0-f387-11e9-9f7f-36d7b8689756&h=957c4d5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%BA%BA%E6%B0%91%E6%97%A5%E5%A0%B1%E6%96%87%E7%AB%A0%E6%89%B9%E8%A9%95%E6%9C%89%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%B8%AD%E5%AD%B8%E6%95%99%E6%9D%90%E5%B0%87%E9%BB%83%E4%B9%8B%E9%8B%92%E5%88%97%E7%82%BA%E5%90%8D%E4%BA%BA%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97-154448827.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25B0%2591%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E6%2596%2587%25E7%25AB%25A0%25E6%2589%25B9%25E8%25A9%2595%25E6%259C%2589%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E6%2595%2599%25E6%259D%2590%25E5%25B0%2587%25E9%25BB%2583%25E4%25B9%258B%25E9%258B%2592%25E5%2588%2597%25E7%2582%25BA%25E5%2590%258D%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%25B3%25BB%25E5%2588%2597-154448827.html&d=IZFSAkWTwbXSesVVmoeERS3KoYHjImyLH66vjnFGY4M%3D&h=b2e4b027\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%BA%BA%E6%B0%91%E6%97%A5%E5%A0%B1%E6%96%87%E7%AB%A0%E6%89%B9%E8%A9%95%E6%9C%89%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%B8%AD%E5%AD%B8%E6%95%99%E6%9D%90%E5%B0%87%E9%BB%83%E4%B9%8B%E9%8B%92%E5%88%97%E7%82%BA%E5%90%8D%E4%BA%BA%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97-154448827.html</a>"},{"pid":"2307797a3faf3b6ea55fb30238a2c3d24c55a6ba","tid":1666272,"uid":253016,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T02:23:32.000Z","msg":"首先 香港人唔係支那豬既同胞<br />\n第二 同乜柒野支那傳統美德一D關係都冇<br />\n第三 見到個中字就眼火爆"},{"pid":"9d66b089122190b209ef17f508aac99b78c0f567","tid":1666272,"uid":10881,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T02:26:00.000Z","msg":"睇字都feel 到廢中教師果種噁心"},{"pid":"75cfda3a4d69a63afe3997fdb30df2668522f6ba","tid":1666272,"uid":33653,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"9d66b089122190b209ef17f508aac99b78c0f567","tid":1666272,"uid":10881,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T02:26:00.000Z","msg":"睇字都feel 到廢中教師果種噁心"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T02:46:00.000Z","msg":"佢無得唔係名人喎。"},{"pid":"1d37a4d78d15bf322295f01df49032677c8c6695","tid":1666272,"uid":83582,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T02:53:42.000Z","msg":"黃之鋒都算港獨份子?"},{"pid":"c29513c121d8816defa334a21b8cec59951ab48e","tid":1666272,"uid":78574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T02:54:36.000Z","msg":"Netflix都有得睇佢你話佢唔係名人呀?"},{"pid":"f472b190009d145de670ddacc30b59bb3ef16b34","tid":1666272,"uid":231480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c29513c121d8816defa334a21b8cec59951ab48e","tid":1666272,"uid":78574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T02:54:36.000Z","msg":"Netflix都有得睇佢你話佢唔係名人呀?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T02:56:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zxPWRGO.png\" dat